channel.title: [2006] Project F 2 P - F2P Remake [2006]
channel.description:
[center][img]http://i779.photobucket.com/albums/yy71/lostmyphat/ftp2006.png[/img]
[b]I've been working on a project like this since the beginning of the summer. I've learned tons of new things and finally decided that I was able to continue this with my new knowledge. The whole reason why I started this is because I could finish it. This is based off a clean Delta, that I completely cleaned out to all F2P content. Our goal is to start with the basics (doors, npcs, drops, dialogue, shops ETC) then start moving onto quests and combat/skills.
I'm trying to learn as much as I can about this base, looking up tutorials etc. Other than me, the founder, Daniel aka zfreak helps A LOT, he has done 85% of the woodcutting and has almost completed mining. He is the same age as me, 14. If you would like to join our team, (Halflive, Acans, Zfreak, Me) PM me.
[/b]
